Goa with him ✈️
A live example of the power of manifestation ❤️
We’re both from totally different cultures and totally regular families.
Getting married was something we thought we’d have to fight for let alone get to come to Goa with all our parents’ happy consensus but your truth always wins!
Over all these years of knowing each other our families have grown to love our personalities and who we are as individuals and how we support each other as a couple.
It may be just another Goa picture for some but for me, it’s a dream come true 💫
Love you @kumar_agarwal ❤️
